{"tid":2093521,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[純FF] 論集資建新香港可能性","createTime":"2020-07-04T01:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T03:59:42.000Z","uid":43718,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"04acf83d8e8ee475c6bf2071212c06a61dc06ea7","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"前言及參考資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbziAhRY4eXE&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=4e3074d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE</a><br />\n<br />\n好草率嘅小小想法<br />\n<br />\n其實好多國家 例如美國加州為例<br />\n有極多土地空置<br />\n有無可能由香港人集資 去租借一定土地發展<br />\nLet&rsquo;s say 有十萬人集資 每人出十萬 已經有一百億<br />\n當然可能要有時間嘅發展等等<br />\n<br />\n當然 你問十個香港人 十個都唔會想走<br />\n但當香港嘅問題已經去到改變唔到嘅嚴重程度<br />\n係咪要作出改變<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Hong Kong is not a place. It&rsquo;s a people</span></span>"},{"pid":"2efc883ad238520b0d0866748a03467b93d6a6f5","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd3d340a850a56f0ef87460b0e381c002ed32d6","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf7f9bcd5f78e2311f3822af9f9573451d2b032","tid":2093521,"uid":55658,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"之前有人講過話以政府派嘅一萬去做基金嘅"},{"pid":"8d447b5eec00ee93dec8317113aaf7fcfb6855a3","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f353696c53c67e1e058272637877b85babc9f364","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite