a href=\"https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbziAhRY4eXE&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=4e3074d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bziAhRY4eXE</a><br />\n<br />\n好草率嘅小小想法<br />\n<br />\n其實好多國家 例如美國加州為例<br />\n有極多土地空置<br />\n有無可能由香港人集資 去租借一定土地發展<br />\nLet&rsquo;s say 有十萬人集資 每人出十萬 已經有一百億<br />\n當然可能要有時間嘅發展等等<br />\n<br />\n當然 你問十個香港人 十個都唔會想走<br />\n但當香港嘅問題已經去到改變唔到嘅嚴重程度<br />\n係咪要作出改變<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Hong Kong is not a place. It&rsquo;s a people</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"點樣帶走現時庫房嗰幾千億？"},{"pid":"555b35d3cbbf49fd27c1f7b64190e57efd0e5f22","tid":2093521,"uid":180499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf110b564f6c84ec04548ecf80ef34cb585563ad","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555b35d3cbbf49fd27c1f7b64190e57efd0e5f22","tid":2093521,"uid":180499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52c8a3a9526d7e7829d2daff74e330ae472ef5c","tid":2093521,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"喺澳洲好過,因為如果根據時區嚟講,可以做返金融中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec71900141c99a83ce4ac22a6b6689f10c84c007","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9e6d7b9f76f9d2f53470acfdb1927b1162d8c3","tid":2093521,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo