ote":{"pid":"07a961c07d1919b100998d35486e63d02dfada80","tid":2093521,"uid":268537,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"香港可以發達係因為政治因素,唔係因為地理位置<br />\n係49年中共建政之前香港只係個正常水平城市<br />\n<br />\n因為中國赤化咗,而上海又死埋<br />\n只係剩翻香港係自由世界唯一華人城市<br />\n導致如果西方想做中國生意只可以經香港<br />\n令到香港集中曬全東亞資源,華人精英走曬落嚟<br />\n所以香港先會發達<br />\n<br />\n而家中美再次脫鈎,唔同嘅係香港成為咗當年嘅上海<br />\n若然西方仍然想與中國做生意<br />\n就只可以去新加坡同台灣(但兩地都唔係最完美替代選擇)<br />\n<br />\n如果想要海外建立新香港,可以考慮下呢個方向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:28:44.000Z","msg":"姐係又比班支那人入黎滲透？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b117759a65d3c70001970cdda3a2626f6c22e8","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4072c5cc4237e7b401bb8bd6dade051f28fae137","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d525b921bdfc409657c55df19b5a35a187b7238","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a038e9f1ac3e8f4041ce22caa6c6b27325cde9cd","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bff8857dc97114f521aaf39a1a3c06e51fe9101","tid":2093521,"uid":127490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"395ae7caf87b98db34f652aed0bba8197bdf43f0","tid":2093521,"uid":92353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"根本係 如果個個去到外地真係當自己移民融入曬 變曬當地人 <br />\n 香港人,廣東話 真係好快絕種"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4dd75a3e874dd2ed0745f2af8251fabb62b4d330","tid":2093521,"uid":127490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:13:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3b5f16e62fa5d5a8c31f777f977a0ad4129d853","tid":2093521,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:13:29.000Z","msg":"租地建政？"},{"pid":"161730807e1877aa880c517f9c84e50a6b84ce34","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4347f5383ca2a4923c15bfe7b2dfe873e0ec9c8","tid":2093521,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"其實去馬拉買地仲好<br />\n1.亞洲 近香港 有戰略位置<br />\n2.有大量未開發土地 可以發展其他工業 經濟<br />\n3.鄰近多發展中國家 可以有大量發展潛力 重新建立亞洲國際金融中心"},{"pid":"61e133c69c21b55bcfa942e85d6976c53b4817ad","tid":2093521,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}